data.description: You'll have quick and easy access to all amenities and services within the city limits. The house boasts beautiful and low-maintenance vinyl plank flooring throughout. A fenced yard adds privacy and security for your family, pets, or a small garden (4 ft in front yard and 5 ft in back). Fresh exterior paint. A great starter home or a perfect retirement retreat! It would make a great Air BnB as well. The owner will replace the roof with an agreed-on contract, and this will be done right before closing.
